metadata.name: Benjamin Hill Mining Corp
metadata.description: Benjamin Hill Mining Corp. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of natural resource properties in Mexico and Canada. The company primarily explores for gold, silver, and copper deposits. It holds interest in the Benjamin Hill property located in the Caborca gold belt; and Sonora Gold property located in the mining district of Benjamin Hill in Sonora, Mexico. The company was formerly known as Mojave Gold Corp. and changed its name to Benjamin Hill Mining Corp. in April 2021. Benjamin Hill Mining Corp. was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Richmond, Canada.
